          <a href="#governing-law" class="text-cyan-400/60 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">06. Governing Law</a>
          <a href="#contact" class="text-cyan-400/60 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">07. Contact Information</a>
